  "instructions": [
    "In a medium bowl, whisk together butter, brown sugar, water, apple cider vinegar, paprika, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper until smooth.",
    "Add wienerschnitzel to the bowl and toss to coat evenly.",
    "Preheat a non-stick skillet or griddle over medium-high heat.",
    "Cook wienerschnitzel for 2-3 minutes per side, or until crispy and golden brown.",
    "Meanwhile, toast buns on the skillet or griddle for 1-2 minutes, or until lightly browned.",
    "Assemble burgers by spreading mustard on the bottom bun, followed by a cooked wienerschnitzel, a lettuce leaf, a tomato slice, a cheese slice, and finally the top bun.",
    "Repeat with remaining wienerschnitzel and ingredients.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
